{"tid":1167192,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[教畜]老師私設「品德部隊」 學生被公審諗過死","createTime":"2019-05-23T01:34:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-23T01:41:21.000Z","uid":56881,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"65351c22323e798f3cf9062d9dbf2ff237dd8f36","tid":1167192,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T01:34:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%80%81%E5%B8%AB%E7%A7%81%E8%A8%AD%E3%80%8C%E5%93%81%E5%BE%B7%E9%83%A8%E9%9A%8A%E3%80%8D%E3%80%80%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E8%A2%AB%E5%85%AC%E5%AF%A9%E8%AB%97%E9%81%8E%E6%AD%BB-235523455.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E8%2580%2581%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E7%25A7%2581%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E3%2580%258C%25E5%2593%2581%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E9%2583%25A8%25E9%259A%258A%25E3%2580%258D%25E3%2580%2580%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25AF%25A9%25E8%25AB%2597%25E9%2581%258E%25E6%25AD%25BB-235523455.html&d=z4MUysNBbosN1Ywc1Uoyoyukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=435622b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%80%81%E5%B8%AB%E7%A7%81%E8%A8%AD%E3%80%8C%E5%93%81%E5%BE%B7%E9%83%A8%E9%9A%8A%E3%80%8D%E3%80%80%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E8%A2%AB%E5%85%AC%E5%AF%A9%E8%AB%97%E9%81%8E%E6%AD%BB-235523455.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/1xzXrXqr_dgz2f0aEnBjXQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9MzY5/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/d14d4ca13cf376443c4a78db1cf3a4fe\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F1xzXrXqr_dgz2f0aEnBjXQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9MzY5%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2Fd14d4ca13cf376443c4a78db1cf3a4fe&h=084740d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n裘錦秋中學(元朗)爆出有老師自設機制懲罰學生，有學生受壓下曾欲輕生。<br />\n<br />\n老師奇招懲罰學生惹關注。裘錦秋中學(元朗)一名老師涉<span style=\"color: red;\">自設「品德培育精鋼部隊」，要求欠交功課、儀容不整的同學入「部隊」改善行為，有學生更被拍攝認錯片段於其他同學前播放</span>，受辱學生難堪受壓，有人甚至有輕生念頭。家長獲悉事件後大感不滿，斥責該名老師「當學生好似犯(人)咁！」校方不認同此做法，指老師的做法未經校方同意也不恰當，已停止該名老師的訓輔工作。教育局並沒接獲家長的相關查詢或投訴，但已聯絡學校要求處理學生紀律問題時顧及自尊及個人差異。 <br />\n<br />\n一名不願透露姓名的家長表示，就讀該校的孩子升讀中五後經常悶悶不樂，曾透露討厭學校及一名老師，並指該名老師經常侮辱同學及不合理地懲罰同學，不少同學對其既厭又怕。該名家長其後在孩子的書包中找到一封信，<span style=\"color: red;\">寫有「品德培育精鋼部隊的部隊執行令」字樣，下款是「部隊總司令」，據知由學校老師發出，信件註明機密信函，要求學生在指定日子準時出席「紀律聆訊會議」，形容是次任務屬高度機密活動，不可向任何人士洩露，否則將遭嚴懲。</span><br />\n<br />\n家長追問下得悉，孩子欠交功課，被發該「機密信函」，又要徵召入相關「部隊」，該名老師曾要求犯錯的學生錄影認錯，片段會在其他同學面前播放，令學生感到尷尬和難受，甚至遭同學嘲笑，其孩子倍感壓力，一度抗拒上學，又曾聲言想自殺，家長憂心不已。<br />\n<br />\n東網向校方查詢，該校溫副校長表示，上述「部隊」是該名老師的個人主意，未經校方批准，學校收到家長匿名投訴信後，已認真處理及向該名老師了解。校方擔心事件影響學生情緒，已立即要求老師停止推行，相關「部隊」已不存在，校方正計劃作出補救。溫又指，該名老師的出發點是期望學生糾正錯誤，但用錯方法，據其所知，要求學生拍片是想要他們講出改善行為的方法及向家長表達感恩，而非要求他們認錯。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/9tjwb0gvHnMBeVVUU7MGLw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NjI4/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/1db717a74e42abc3f117f4e73714a29a\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F9tjwb0gvHnMBeVVUU7MGLw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NjI4%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F1db717a74e42abc3f117f4e73714a29a&h=41302458&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n家長發現「品德培育精鋼部隊」的信件，才知道有老師怪招懲罰其子女。(受訪者提供)<br />\n<br />\n睇得秘密警察太多?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e5d2feabc7460565c745fc5c50dbd9cc8db3839","tid":1167192,"uid":245441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T01:35:41.000Z","msg":"譚道德?"},{"pid":"cdfd571e6473b03d6d44c26a676c365a35758381","tid":1167192,"uid":178187,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T01:36:01.000Z","msg":"文革2.0"},{"pid":"0c2969e51cfed65304e56a9d77e493f9da8a34a0","tid":1167192,"uid":224510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T01:36:52.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c78ab9809c0bfe7505e3bcbe91af92823fa92090","tid":1167192,"uid":8410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T01:39:46.000Z","msg":"教書教到痴左線"},{"pid":"54fc540d9b0af6d7843ebe6e12ba81d6777ab2a3","tid":1167192,"uid":49588,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T01:41:15.000Z","msg":"甚麼令？！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n成個支那特色制度。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42ffe2687ba973bfc2411c705cdefb7e2ab72706","tid":1167192,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c78ab9809c0bfe7505e3bcbe91af92823fa92090","tid":1167192,"uid":8410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T01:39:46.000Z","msg":"教書教到痴左線"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T01:41:21.000Z","msg":"以為自己好撚大權"}]}